      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study with Richardson extrapolation. GCI_fine = 1.7% on hemolysis index QoI, well within the 5% threshold for MRL 2. Monotonic convergence confirmed (ratio 0.98). Production runs use 5.8M cell mesh providing adequate accuracy-cost balance. See ValidationResult vr-02-mesh-convergence."
