      "rationale": "Scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. Numerical solver error is subsumed within the code verification activity (factor: Numerical code verification) which demonstrated second-order convergence. Residual convergence to 1e-6 confirmed for all production runs, providing sufficient assurance that iterative solver errors are negligible relative to discretization and model form uncertainties."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
