      "rationale": "All model inputs (geometry, fluid properties, boundary conditions, hemolysis model coefficients) traceable to documented sources. Pump geometry from certified CAD file (revision-controlled). Blood analog properties from ASTM F1841. Hemolysis model coefficients from Giersiepen et al. 1990 as standardized in FDA guidance. Inlet boundary conditions derived from clinical CPB flow specifications with ±5% uncertainty quantified in Monte Carlo analysis."
    },
    {
