      "rationale": "Scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. Validation uses published FDA benchmark dataset (Hariharan et al. 2011) with n=3 replicate measurements per operating point, which is the standard dataset for this class of device. Formal test sample adequacy assessment (e.g., statistical power analysis for sample size) is not required at MRL 2. Dataset provenance and traceability documented."
