      "rationale": "Scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. Input parameters used in validation (geometry, fluid properties, operating conditions) are directly matched to the FDA benchmark experimental conditions. No parameter translation or equivalency mapping is required because simulation inputs are set to match experimental conditions exactly. Formal equivalency assessment not required at this model risk level."
